" y$ -> Y Make Y behave like other capitals
inoremap Y y$

" Mimic Emacs Line Editing in Insert Mode Only
inoremap <C-A> <Home>
inoremap <C-E> <End>
inoremap <C-B> <Left>
inoremap <C-F> <Right>

" Insert mode commands for quick deletion
inoremap <C-D> <S-BS>
inoremap <C-C> <ESC>

" Insert mode quick move
inoremap <C-H> <S-Left>
inoremap <C-L> <S-Right>
inoremap <C-J> <Down>
inoremap <C-K> <Up>

